    <h5>Your Choices</h5>

    <p><span>You may choose not to provide certain personal information, but this may limit your ability to use certain features of the App.</span></p>

    <p><span>You may also opt-out of receiving promotional emails from us by following the unsubscribe instructions in the email.</span></p>

